Airport malaria - Australia (02) 970324114752
>Is it not the case that in the last ?5 years indigenous transmission
of P.vivax has already been reported in the North Queensland
area (? on an an island off the coast) and not associated with
aircraft?
>D.C.Warhurst
<david.warhurst@lshtm.ac.uk>
